M|EOS |tx|Implementing EOS transforms companies across every industry. This collection of case studies illustrates how different tp of organizations -- from SaaS startups to manufacturing companies -- used the Entrepreneurial Operating sy to overcome specific challenges and achieve measurable results. Each case follows a consistent structure and concludes w/ lessons that apply broadly.
M|Tabl|1. [|CloudStack Solutions (SaaS Startup)](#case-study-1-cloudstack-solutions-saas-startup)
M|Tabl|2. [|Meridian Consulting Group (Professional Services)](#case-study-2-meridian-consulting-group-professional-services)
M|Tabl|3. [|Precision Metal Works (Manufacturing)](#case-study-3-precision-metal-works-manufacturing)
M|Tabl|4. [|Spark Digital Agency (mk Agency)](#case-study-4-spark-digital-agency-mk-agency)
M|Tabl|5. [|Summit Health Partners (Healthcare)](#case-study-5-summit-health-partners-healthcare)
M|Tabl|tx|6. [Common Patterns in Successful EOS Implementations](#common-patterns-in-successful-eos-implementations)
